{"lemma":"مُكَسَّر","slug":"مُكَسَّر","root":"ك.س.ر","root_slug":"ك-س-ر","root_link":"/words/roots/ك-س-ر","pos":"ADJ","pos_camel":"adj","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n36981","n36983"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%85%D9%8F%D9%83%D9%8E%D8%B3%D9%8E%D9%91%D8%B1"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n36981","headword_ar":"مَكْسِرٌ","root":"ksr","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A place of breaking,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,) of anything. (TA.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EuwdN Sulobu Almakosiri","text_ar":"عُودٌ صُلْبُ المَكْسِرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Wood,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a piece of wood,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a branch,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"twig, hard in the place of breaking,"},{"kind":"text","text":"] when you know its goodness by its breaking: (S, A:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EuwdN","text_ar":"عُودٌ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tay~ibu Almakosiri","text_ar":"طَيِّبُ المَكْسِرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Wood,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"good in the place of breaking,"},{"kind":"text","text":"] i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"approved."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) ―         -b2-  Hence,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rajulN","text_ar":"رَجُلٌ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sulobu Almakosiri","text_ar":"صُلْبُ المَكْسِرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, L) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A man who bears up"},{"kind":"page_break","n":2613},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"against difficulty, distress,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"adversity:"},{"kind":"text","text":"because one breaks a piece of wood, to try if it be hard or soft. (TA.) And of a pl. number,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"humo","text_ar":"هُمْ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SilaAbu AlmakaAsiri","text_ar":"صِلَابُ المَكَاسِرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (A.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnN ha$~u Almakosiri","text_ar":"فُلَانٌ هَشُّ المَكْسِرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Almukas~ari","text_ar":"المُكَسَّرِ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"h$","text_ar":"هش"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v.,) (assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one is easy,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"compliant, when asked"},{"kind":"text","text":"], which is an expression of praise when it means [lit.] that he is not one whose wood gives only a sound when one endeavours to produce fire from it; and of dispraise when it means [lit.] that be is one whose wood is weak. (TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnN Tay~ibu","text_ar":"فُلَانٌ طَيِّبُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Almakosiri","text_ar":"المَكْسِرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one is praised when tried, proved,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tested:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"radiYo'u Almakosiri","text_ar":"رَدِىْءُ المَكْسِرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dispraised when tried,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.]. (TA.) [Wherefore it is said that]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"makosirN","text_ar":"مَكْسِرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies (assumed tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"internal state; an internal,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"intrinsic, quality;"},{"kind":"text","text":"the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"intrinsic,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"real, as opposed to the apparent, state,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to the aspect;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maxobarN","text_ar":"مَخْبَرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) ―         -b3-  Also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"makosirN","text_ar":"مَكْسِرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lowest part"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aSolN","text_ar":"اَصْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"K, TA) of anything; and especially of a tree,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"where the branches are broken off."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b4-  [Hence] it is said to be metonymically used as meaning (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Old property."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faroEN","text_ar":"فَرْعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b5-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kasorN","text_ar":"كَسْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["K","TA","S","A","L"]},{"entry_id":"n36983","headword_ar":"مُكَسَّرٌ","root":"ksr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"pass. part. n. of 2, q. v. ―         -b2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"makosirN","text_ar":"مَكْسِرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", with which it is made synonymous. ―         -b3-  (tropical:)  A valley"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"whose"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kusuwr","text_ar":"كُسُور"},{"kind":"text","text":"(q. v.)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"flow with water:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"are made to flow:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Th:) accord. to one relation of a saying in which it occurs, it is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mukosarN","text_ar":"مُكْسَرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["K","Th"]}]}}